    <title type="html"><![CDATA[HTML5]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.bujiang.info/blog/2013/11/29/html5/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-29T07:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.bujiang.info/blog/2013/11/29/html5</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>HTML5相较于HTML 4.01还是挺多相当省事的变化</p>

<p>DOCTYPE在HTML 4.01里
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4.01 Strict </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="ni">&amp;lt;</span>!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;&amp;ndash;</span>//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span> <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;</span><span class="nt">&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>strict.dtd<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span>&gt;
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4.01 Transitional </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="ni">&amp;lt;</span>!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;&amp;ndash;</span>//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span> <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;</span><span class="nt">&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>http://<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span>&gt;
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4.01 Frameset </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="ni">&amp;lt;</span>!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;&amp;ndash;</span>//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Frameset//EN<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span> <span class="ni">&amp;ldquo;</span><span class="nt">&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://www.w3.org/&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>http://www.w3.org/<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>TR/html4/frameset.dtd<span class="ni">&amp;rdquo;</span>&gt;
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>在HTML 5中就相当简单了
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 5 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="ni">&amp;lt;</span>!DOCTYPE html&gt;
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>META
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">http-equiv=</span><span class="s">&quot;Content-Type&quot;</span> <span class="na">content=</span><span class="s">&quot;text/html; charset=UTF-8&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 5 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;meta</span> <span class="na">charset=</span><span class="s">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>Script Tag
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4.01 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;script </span><span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span> <span class="na">src=</span><span class="s">&quot;file.js&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div><br/>
在HTML 5中省去了type 浏览器会推测使用的是javascript
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 5 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;script </span><span class="na">src=</span><span class="s">&quot;file.js&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>Link Tag
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 4.01 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">&quot;text/css&quot;</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;file.css&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>对于Link Tag同样也可以省去type
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>HTML 5 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">&quot;file.css&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
